summary: I’ve been so excited to show you all this piece I did for the @uravitybang collaboration piece. In the last few months I’ve been...
caption:
I’ve been so excited to show you all this piece I did for the @uravitybang collaboration piece. In the last few months I’ve been working together with some amazing writers to create 2 pieces for the event. 

 Here’s my response piece for @officialao3fandomlastforever’s written piece ‘Diary of the Gravity Ghost’. They were amazing to work with and I highly recommend checking out their piece, it was so good 💖💖💖
